Package: lisi
Type: Package
Title: Local Inverse Simpson Index (LISI) for scRNAseq data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-03-31
Author: Ilya Korsunsky
Maintainer: Ilya Korsunsky <ilya.korsunsky@gmail.com>
Description: This method was designed to assess how well mixed cells with
    different labels are in single cell RNAseq. This method uses the Inverse
    Simpson's Index to compute diversity of each cell's local neighborhood.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Imports: Rcpp, RANN
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Suggests: testthat, dplyr, tidyr, magrittr, ggplot2
NeedsCompilation: yes
LazyData: true
Encoding: UTF-8
